                      <p class="style79"><strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> Regulators meet IT directors: </em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong><em><em><em><em><em> With the increasing movement of government to adopt IT-based tools and solutions has come a need for companies to get on the same band wagon &ndash; or else. The following selection of articles from around the world focus on the issue of regulatory compliance, using standards-based (and mandated) systems. </em></em></em></em></em></p></td>
